## Recommendation

**Go with the 3-level taxonomy** because:

✅ **Better for RAG**: Clear hierarchical structure improves semantic search and context retrieval  
✅ **Scalability**: Easy to add new content without restructuring  
✅ **User-friendly**: Logical grouping makes navigation intuitive  
✅ **Content Management**: Clear ownership and maintenance responsibility  
✅ **Reduces Duplication**: Clear categorization prevents duplicate content creation  

The 3-level structure provides enough depth for precise categorization while avoiding over-complexity.
